manifestWithDefaults:
builder:
  track: dev
labels:
  app: estafette-ci-web
  app-group: estafette-ci
  language: nodejs
  team: estafette-team
version:
  semver:

stages:
  restore:
    image: node:10.9.0-alpine
    shell: /bin/sh
    workDir: /estafette-work
    commands:
    - npm install
    when: status == 'succeeded'
  unit-test:
    image: node:10.9.0-alpine
    shell: /bin/sh

  build:

  bake:
